    <item>
      <title>据称 Axiata 和 Sinar Mas 即将达成收购印尼子公司的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/axiata-sinar-mas-are-said-to-near-deal-for-indonesian-units</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，马来西亚无线运营商 Axiata Group Bhd. 与印尼企业集团 PT Sinar Mas Group 即将达成协议，合并双方在东南亚最大经济体的电信业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/axiata-sinar-mas-are-said-to-near-deal-for-indonesian-units</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 10:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的保罗谈地缘政治和中国战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/morgan-stanley-s-paul-on-geopolitics-china-s-strategy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利高级投资组合经理 Sherry Paul 讨论了当前的地缘政治事件如何影响投资环境。Paul 告诉彭博电视台：“那些持久的、支撑增长和收益的主题将推动市场走高，这就是为什么我们现在在投资中仍然以美国为中心。”她还讨论了中国的货币政策立场及其对投资组合的影响。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/morgan-stanley-s-paul-on-geopolitics-china-s-strategy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 10:05:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受制裁的俄罗斯油轮绕道英国返回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/sanctioned-russia-oil-tanker-turns-back-from-detour-around-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘从波罗的海向印度运送俄罗斯原油的油轮被发现驶往设得兰群岛 —— 这条路线本来会绕过英国北端 —— 但油轮突然转向，选择了一条更为典型的航程，穿越英吉利海峡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/sanctioned-russia-oil-tanker-turns-back-from-detour-around-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 10:03:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GIC 选择摩根大通为 Greenko 50 亿美元股权出售提供咨询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/gic-picks-jpmorgan-to-advise-on-5-billion-greenko-stake-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，新加坡政府投资公司 (GIC Pte) 正与摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 合作，帮助其对多项选择进行战略评估，其中包括出售其在印度 Greenko Energy Holdings 的 50% 股份，这可能是印度最大的资产出售案之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/gic-picks-jpmorgan-to-advise-on-5-billion-greenko-stake-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 09:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农业信贷银行采取行动捍卫利益，BPM 银行股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/banco-bpm-rises-as-credit-agricole-moves-to-shore-up-interests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 采取措施增加其在 Banco BPM SpA 的股份，该银行的股价上涨至近九年来的最高水平，而该银行目前正在与 UniCredit SpA 的主动收购行为进行竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/banco-bpm-rises-as-credit-agricole-moves-to-shore-up-interests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:27:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其建筑股因叙利亚重建押注而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/turkish-building-stocks-surge-on-syria-reconstruction-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以水泥和钢铁制造商为首的土耳其建筑相关类股飙升，因为投资者押注这些公司将在巴沙尔·阿萨德政权迅速垮台后在邻国叙利亚的重建中发挥关键作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/turkish-building-stocks-surge-on-syria-reconstruction-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:17:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市、人民币尾盘反弹，因政治局作出承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/chinese-stocks-yuan-stage-late-rebound-on-politburo-pledges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于国家高层领导人承诺放松货币政策并扩大财政支出，在香港上市的中国股票在交易的最后一个小时出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/chinese-stocks-yuan-stage-late-rebound-on-politburo-pledges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:41:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普回归 中国暗示明年将推出更大胆刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-shifts-monetary-policy-stance-for-first-time-since-2011</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着北京方面为唐纳德·特朗普上任后可能爆发的贸易战做好准备，中国高层领导人计划在 2025 年放松货币政策并扩大财政支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-shifts-monetary-policy-stance-for-first-time-since-2011</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工会谈判进入第四轮 大众汽车遭遇更多罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/vw-faces-more-costly-walkouts-as-union-talks-enter-fourth-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车公司 (Volkswagen AG) 工人于周一举行罢工，工会领导人威胁称，如果大众同名品牌的裁员计划未能取得突破，他们将升级抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/vw-faces-more-costly-walkouts-as-union-talks-enter-fourth-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治因素抵消中国带动的提振作用，股市波动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东和韩国的政治动荡削弱了人们对中国货币政策转变的乐观情绪，且投资者等待几个关键市场的央行决定，欧洲股市和美国期货难以确定方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 22:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
